&lt;h3 id="Do-not-assume-others-get-it-right"&gt;Do not assume others get it right&lt;a class="anchor-link" href="http://carreau.github.io/posts/12-Write-An-IPython-Kernel.ipynb.html#Do-not-assume-others-get-it-right"&gt;¶&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class="cell border-box-sizing text_cell rendered"&gt;
